room_title: Escape room "Kraken the Case" by Zero Hour Escape Rooms in Minneapolis - St. Paul
room_address: 12800 Industrial Park Boulevard Suite #130 Minneapolis, MN 55441
room_description:
Jimmy B’s Tiki Bar is a Key West staple. The owner, Tallahassee Jenkins, is well respected in the area, as is his bar. However, there is trouble brewing in paradise- and we’re not talking about the IPA’s! Over the past few weeks, 4 employees have gone missing! With the local police scratching their heads and the town in a panic, Tallahassee has hired a team of investigators to look into the disappearances. That’s where you come in.

You and your team are the only hope if this bar is to keep its reputation. Tallahassee doesn’t want the town to panic, so he plans to open the bar at its usual time. You’ll be working against the clock!

You have one hour…
